<!-- Hard to distinguish between oganisation and public transpot system, therefore properties from both domains are used. -->
{{TemplateMapping
| mapToClass = PublicTransitSystem
| mappings =
	{{ PropertyMapping | templateProperty = name | ontologyProperty = foaf:name }}
	{{ PropertyMapping | templateProperty = logo | ontologyProperty = foaf:logo }}
	{{ PropertyMapping | templateProperty = company_slogan | ontologyProperty = slogan }}
	{{ PropertyMapping | templateProperty = parent | ontologyProperty = owner }}
	{{ PropertyMapping | templateProperty = founded | ontologyProperty = openingDate }}
	{{ PropertyMapping | templateProperty = founded | ontologyProperty = openingYear }}
	{{ PropertyMapping | templateProperty = defunct | ontologyProperty = closingDate }}
	{{ PropertyMapping | templateProperty = defunct | ontologyProperty = closingYear }}
	{{ PropertyMapping | templateProperty = headquarters | ontologyProperty = headquarter }}
	{{ PropertyMapping | templateProperty = locale | ontologyProperty = location }}
	{{ PropertyMapping | templateProperty = service_area | ontologyProperty = regionServed }}
	{{ PropertyMapping | templateProperty = service_type | ontologyProperty = type }}
	{{ PropertyMapping | templateProperty = alliance | ontologyProperty = isPartOf }}
	{{ PropertyMapping | templateProperty = routes | ontologyProperty = numberOfLines }}
	{{ PropertyMapping | templateProperty = destinations | ontologyProperty = regionServed }}
	{{ PropertyMapping | templateProperty = stops | ontologyProperty = numberOfStations }}
	{{ PropertyMapping | templateProperty = stations | ontologyProperty = numberOfStations }}
	<!-- {{ PropertyMapping | templateProperty = hubs | ontologyProperty = ??? }} -->
	<!-- {{ PropertyMapping | templateProperty = lounge | ontologyProperty = ??? }} -->
	<!-- {{ PropertyMapping | templateProperty = depots | ontologyProperty = ??? }} -->
	{{ PropertyMapping | templateProperty = fleet | ontologyProperty = numberOfVehicles }}
	{{ PropertyMapping | templateProperty = ridership | ontologyProperty = passengersPerDay }}
	{{ PropertyMapping | templateProperty = annual ridership | ontologyProperty = passengersPerYear }}
	{{ PropertyMapping | templateProperty = annual_ridership | ontologyProperty = passengersPerYear }}
	<!-- {{ PropertyMapping | templateProperty = fuel_type | ontologyProperty = ??? }} -->
	{{ PropertyMapping | templateProperty = operator | ontologyProperty = operatedBy }}
	<!-- {{ PropertyMapping | templateProperty = ceo | ontologyProperty = ??? }} -->
	<!-- {{ PropertyMapping | templateProperty = leader | ontologyProperty = ??? }} -->
	{{ PropertyMapping | templateProperty = website | ontologyProperty = foaf:homepage }}
}}
